  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hydrogen</h2> is a Roguelite Action Game In a Sci-Fi post-apocalyptic landscape where humanity teeters on the brink, you step into the boots of a fearless Mercenary with a mission to rescue the world from impending doom.<br>Procedural generated instances, offering a fresh and unpredictable challenge each time you play.<br>Level up your Mercenary with perks at every turn, enhancing your abilities and customizing your playstyle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Elemental Attacks :</strong></h2>-<strong>Physical </strong>: Raw Damage<br>-<strong>Fire </strong>: Damage over time that scales with Player Power<br>-<strong>Acid </strong>: Damage over time that scales with Enemy Health<br>-<strong>Electric </strong>: Multi Target Damage that scales with Power<br>-<strong>Frost </strong>: Stuns Enemies<br>-<strong>Void </strong>: Knocks Back Enemies<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Parrying Attacks :</strong></h2>Performing a parry reflects the exact enemy attack!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746820/extras/7b3cf3ad9ffb2ccba8e5175771d0270a.poster.avif?t=1763565131\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746820/extras/7b3cf3ad9ffb2ccba8e5175771d0270a.webm?t=1763565131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746820/extras/7b3cf3ad9ffb2ccba8e5175771d0270a.mp4?t=1763565131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746820/extras/83d217a790cab4236ca638ebb53862d1.poster.avif?t=1763565131\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746820/extras/83d217a790cab4236ca638ebb53862d1.webm?t=1763565131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746820/extras/83d217a790cab4236ca638ebb53862d1.mp4?t=1763565131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746820/extras/21283dbf7e987384eb441bb8fd5d8405.poster.avif?t=1763565131\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746820/extras/21283dbf7e987384eb441bb8fd5d8405.webm?t=1763565131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746820/extras/21283dbf7e987384eb441bb8fd5d8405.mp4?t=1763565131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Dashing</strong> makes the player invulnerable to damage during the dash.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hydrogen</h2> is a Roguelite Action Game In a Sci-Fi post-apocalyptic landscape where humanity teeters on the brink, you step into the boots of a fearless Mercenary with a mission to rescue the world from impending doom.<br>Procedural generated instances, offering a fresh and unpredictable challenge each time you play.<br>Level up your Mercenary with perks at every turn, enhancing your abilities and customizing your playstyle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Elemental Attacks :</strong></h2>-<strong>Physical </strong>: Raw Damage<br>-<strong>Fire </strong>: Damage over time that scales with Player Power<br>-<strong>Acid </strong>: Damage over time that scales with Enemy Health<br>-<strong>Electric </strong>: Multi Target Damage that scales with Power<br>-<strong>Frost </strong>: Stuns Enemies<br>-<strong>Void </strong>: Knocks Back Enemies<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Parrying Attacks :</strong></h2>Performing a parry reflects the exact enemy attack!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746820/extras/7b3cf3ad9ffb2ccba8e5175771d0270a.poster.avif?t=1763565131\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746820/extras/7b3cf3ad9ffb2ccba8e5175771d0270a.webm?t=1763565131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746820/extras/7b3cf3ad9ffb2ccba8e5175771d0270a.mp4?t=1763565131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746820/extras/83d217a790cab4236ca638ebb53862d1.poster.avif?t=1763565131\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746820/extras/83d217a79